                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names (St Mary in <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/>, <ref target="#ms_i1.5"/>); titles and numbers of the Psalms, Canticles and Songs; 
                           title and incipit of the daily readings of <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/>; the names and traditional interpretation of Hebrew letters in Psalm 118; 
                           refrains of <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/> and <ref target="#ms_i1.5"/> (written out fully or abbreviated); a few single words in <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/> and <ref target="#ms_i1.5"/>; elements of the
                           punctuation marks and text dividers; Ethiopic numerals or their
                           elements. A few lines on the opening page of <ref target="#ms_i1.1"/>; a few lines (alternating with black lines) on the incipit page of <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/>.</seg>
                     </handNote>
